```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant HWO as HydrateWorkingOrdersFromBroker
    participant AMO as AdoptMasterOrders
    participant ISV as IsValidMasterOrderState
    participant EMK as ExtractMasterOrderKey
    participant RTD as RouteOrderToMasterDict
    participant DICT as Tracking Dictionaries
    
    HWO->>AMO: Call (master account adoption)
    loop For each order in Account.Orders
        AMO->>AMO: Filter by instrument
        AMO->>ISV: Validate order state
        ISV-->>AMO: true/false
        alt State valid
            AMO->>AMO: ClassifyOrderByPrefix
            alt Classification valid
                AMO->>EMK: Extract dictionary key
                EMK-->>AMO: key (e.g., "MOMO_001")
                AMO->>RTD: Route to dictionary
                RTD->>DICT: Write order to dict
                RTD-->>AMO: Increment adoptedCount
            end
        end
    end
    AMO-->>HWO: Return adoptedCount
```

